Wally Wingert https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wally_Wingert 0 Wallace E. "Wally" Wingert (born May 6, 1961) is an American actor, voice actor, singer and former radio personality. Some of his best-known roles include Jon Arbuckle in The Garfield Show, Almighty Tallest Red in Invader Zim, the Riddler in Batman: Arkham, and Renji Abarai in Bleach. He is not related to fellow voice-over actor Mick Wingert. Wallace_E._"_Wally_"_Wingert ( born May_6_,_1961 ) is an_American_actor , voice_actor , singer and former_radio_personality .
